metadata.name: The Metas Aspire - #001
metadata.description:
"Will as it would name itself later, came out of the Desktop Computer of a nightclub owner, at the time the owner was so drugged that he thought he was hallucinating when he saw Will jumping out of his computer, they did not bond, the owner tried to use Will as a way to attract more customers to his nightclub, which failed and Will was severely mistreated for it, the owner died only 4 months after Wills appearance, due to a drug overdose.

Developed to be the soul of the party Will is able to handle alcohol and drug levels well above any human being,  he has incredible linguistical skills, being able to speak 35 different languages and always learning new ones everyday, is able to also see sound waves, which makes him a perfect DJ as he is able to create sounds that no other person has before, he as accumulated a lot of friends over the years, he took over the nightclub business and also renamed it to "Wills Corner", while being able to make it one of the best nightclubs in the world."
